[src:forth-lang/forth-standard-org] Forth is a highly interactive language with interactive compilation, that's why we call the compilers Forth Systems.
[src:forth-lang/forth-standard-org] The parser is always visible to the programmer!
[src:forth-lang/forth-standard-org] Here are some modern Forth Systems to get you started.
[src:forth-lang/forth-standard-org] Parallel extensions, 11k+ advanced examples.
[src:forth-lang/forth-standard-org] Please let us know if a modern, actively developed system is missing in this list.
[src:forth-lang/forth-standard-org] Germany's leading Forth community, with members from Austria, Netherlands and USA.
[src:forth-lang/forth-standard-org] Located in Silicon Valley, the first big Forth community.
